com.jrfom.gw2.api.model.items

Class InfixUpgrade

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jrfom.gw2.api.model.items.InfixUpgrade

  • public class InfixUpgrade
extends Object
    Represents permanent upgrades to an item. For example, in-game armor that has "Power", "Toughness", and "Vitality" upgrades would have an InfixUpgrade property that has three attributes.
